  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd - \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9 ?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "What was discussed between President Ranil and Leader of Opposition Sajith?",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa said that he met President Ranil Wickremesinghe after his swearing-in and had a smooth and direct exchange of views.",
        "Ranil Wickramasinghe, who was elected as the 8th Executive President of the country through the parliamentary vote, was sworn in at the Parliament on Thursday 21st.",
        "Accordingly, the Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa, who met President Ranil Wickramasinghe, said the above in a post on his official Twitter page. In the post, he added:",
        "I met President Ranil Wickramasinghe today (yesterday) during the party leaders' meeting. During this there was a smooth and direct exchange of ideas between us. At the same time, I reaffirmed the commitment of the Opposition to provide the effective cooperation necessary to overcome the current crisis.",
        "He said in the recording that instead of providing a large number of ministerial positions to allow political opportunists to waste the country's national resources, he suggested to the president that the parliamentary committee system could be further strengthened to achieve national expectations."
      ],
